Class TransactionQueryBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.insynsregistret.TransactionQueryBuilder
public class TransactionQueryBuilder extends Object
Builder class for creating a query for searching inside trade transactions via the Insynsregistret class.
